Installation
------------
Goinstall is probably the best method of installing goncurses.

goinstall "goncurses.googlecode.com/hg/goncurses"

Alternatively you could use mercurial to install goncurses.

Usage
-----

import "goncurses.googlecode.com/hg/goncurses"

